DESCRIPTION:-
Inspired from the famous game,Flappy Bird we bring to you the most adorable,interesting and adventurous Tappy Plane. Lot of games like this but the best is always on the top. Tappy Plane Ultimate is filled with Challenges. Lot of mountains ,terrains, fields and ofcourse planes to play with. To help you we have Powerups which will astonishingly help you get through difficult times.Tap your plane to rise in the sky and go up. Make your way through the difficult paths of the mountain. This is an endless runner game.Shrink your plane or create a force field around your plane or even amke your plane invisible,Its all there. We gave you 6 new field to explore and 11 new planes to glide your way through Mountains. Take your fun to the next level and pass your time with a blast. 
Tappy Plane Ultimaten, its all what everyone wanted.
